{"tid":1539752,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭回應總結 兩句重點","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:20:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:21:09.000Z","uid":317865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"60bf54b2e6b9e9265d218881937ab8a4319d75d2","tid":1539752,"uid":317865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4jtU4MQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4jtU4MQ.png&h=571935b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#ALERT 消息︰林鄭指不會成立獨立調查委員會 (9/4/17:08) <br />\n<br />\n如果三個月前出可能就或者收貨 <br />\n屌你老母而家先出 想我哋收住貨袋住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不了 收皮啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n8人<br />\n3👁<br />\n&gt;1000手足<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支持香港警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n還黑警一個清白<br />\n捉撚晒啲冚家剷出嚟<br />\n<br />\n恭喜各位狗仔留在歷史中 成為歷史罪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a98cf2c2c454b641abd7d0c7dfa88377b4dd32","tid":1539752,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:21:09.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既